# Machine-local config — paths and secrets. Never commit.
coga.local.toml

# Vendored CLI — refreshed by `coga init --update` from upstream.
.coga/

# Single coga-vendored umbrella. Everything inside is upstream-managed and
# overwritten on every `coga init --update` — your edits will be lost.
# User content goes outside this dir (skills/<your-ns>/, contexts/<your-ns>/).
bootstrap/

# Generated merged skill view for agent CLIs. Rebuilt by `coga init`,
# `coga init --update`, and `coga launch`.
.agent-skills/

# Per-domain scaffolding templates (bare `_template`, `_template.md`).
# Refreshed wholesale on update.
**/_template/
**/_template.md
